text: Elite Model Management (MM) is a modeling agency. It was created in Paris in 1972. In 2004, the agencies in New York City, Miami, Los Angeles, and Toronto are known as Elite Model Management North America. Elite MM is a subsidiary of Elite World S.A.. Although Elite Model Management North America and Elite World Group share the same logo, they have separate ownership and are not part of a business network. ==References== Category:Companies based in Paris Category:Modeling agencies
